(16,'wc-admin-optimizing-the-checkout-flow','info','en_US','Optimizing the checkout flow','It’s crucial to get your store’s checkout as smooth as possible to avoid losing sales. Let’s take a look at how you can optimize the checkout experience for your shoppers.','{}','pending','woocommerce.com','2021-09-24 19:23:22',NULL,0,'plain','',0,'info',0),
